Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去会会他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲爱的奥兹小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然大部分重新编排了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这个八音盒是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H666666&\b0\pos(319,372)\blur5}关于某个随从的死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的曲子怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是稍微有点在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹那首曲子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想问问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是艾略特和里奥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人放学后总是会去合奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该去哪里找他们两个?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:03:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…因为今天已经没有课了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同学们应该是回宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 他们也有可能在图书室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图书室?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到不明人士了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎不在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们去四号楼找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找艾略特他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥就在这里等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是贝萨流士的府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不一定有这么多藏书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是『圣骑士物语』的特别篇!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 在我消失的十年里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了很多我不知道的刊物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很在意它的续集啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想现在就在这里读啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一本不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢这个故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也最～喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是那个圣骑士的随从
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.03,0:04:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说随从艾德格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就是艾德格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个无论何时都更珍视别人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是为了保护别人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不顾自己的伟大的人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在读者中那么有人气 毫无疑问嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:05:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌艾德格那个垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先说话都那么自命不凡 让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我牺牲什么的也很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有在作品中没理由地被人仰慕 让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我喜欢居然还这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最让人不满的就是他的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃生命保护主人 一个人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不过是自我满足罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德格…死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是16卷的中间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是严重的剧透啊啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他的粉丝的话 应该读到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是有10年的空白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁管你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你没读的错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那边两位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能请你们稍微安静一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在约瑟费卢在关键的时刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别插嘴 里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为刚刚是艾略特的不对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剧透
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界上 最让人无法原谅的行为之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你应该道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地像个男子汉一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了…矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是站在哪边的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随从的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常应该帮主人的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改正主人的言行也是随从的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 原来…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要的是对主人言听计从的好随从吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为能和你好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也没那么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我名字和学号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这笔账我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人应该是刚才引起骚动的入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和目击情报一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你没马上说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 因为他看起来不像坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你真的把我当做主人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}好像变复杂了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 这个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前也该说过的 艾达·贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要随便叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对学姐这么说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}好烦 你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 怎么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:08:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识这个入侵者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次入侵事件的犯人好像是你叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是英雄贝萨流士的子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以随心所欲 真让人羡慕!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我去一趟校长室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明刚刚才觉察到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少那么自大地说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不服气的话就来抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹和那个呆瓜妹妹在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左右确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来 笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去和奥兹会合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个味道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是肉的香味!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好… -_-||
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像和贝萨流士家有仇一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长好帅好成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以做你的粉丝吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日是什么时候啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅长的科目是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下个休假有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀～～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅～～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校可真大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得快点找到大家会合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因为艾略特的事生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他很讨厌我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上他是个非常温柔可靠的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要问的问过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要问的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说过 关于艾略特弹的钢琴有事要问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾略特? 钢琴?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都忘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再去找他们一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 别走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对比自己大的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:10:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不自觉就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hello 奥兹小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和姐姐来做有趣的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 我们烤肉部成立以来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首次迎来一位女部员 真是值得纪念的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 开庆功宴了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小猫们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在校内喵喵的很吵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是巴司卡瓦…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为我们是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为是些无赖的话 总有办法逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们又想把我堕入阿嵬茨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为了和小朋友你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相深入了解一下才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次在百忙之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找你出来真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹·贝萨流士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无意加害于你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在你能听从我们的要求的前提下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:12:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的事都告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你在想什么 在希望什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔地告诉大姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想对哥哥做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为风纪委员 我决不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个吵闹的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人质给我安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对艾达做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给她喝了毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要这么做!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 好可怜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事跟艾达没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们威胁我不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想要达成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高效率地…懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个只是墙壁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是入侵者和你们的主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:05.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是墙壁 而是烛台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有什么机关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个学校以前做过要塞和监狱之类的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该是当时的统治者 建造的秘密通道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你准备怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么刚才开始你就不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么由我发问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你珍视的人有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你的死才能解救她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有别的办法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会毫不犹豫地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小朋友 你和那家伙一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的哦 你的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是公认的加害者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是非常恶劣的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要不伤害任何人活下去是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来才是正题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解毒剂我放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要想办法让我们想要用它就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 你想从我这里打听些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是沙布利耶之悲剧的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙布利耶之悲剧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巴司卡瓦制造的大屠杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上我们也在那里杀了不少人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是服从格连大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连理由都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就做出了那种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格连大人的命令是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦下达命令 就无法违抗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想知道详细情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问寄宿在你身体里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小朋友的身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克·贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次我身体虚弱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也没出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定在悠闲地睡午觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再不现身的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你重要的小朋友就要有麻烦了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你恨杰克的话就杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就满足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种自我牺牲保护不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的罪孽太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都会不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是加害者哦 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不是迷路的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小弟弟 有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,履行见到这一幕的人的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个都跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人不是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巴司卡瓦的子民吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在连这种小孩都知道这名字了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴司卡瓦是100年前的大罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨伐他们对贵族而言 是使命 也是最大的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你没任何关系!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 快跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 你这个艾德格式的家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怕受伤害算什么强大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不过是连背负责任都做不到的人说的胡话!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴司卡瓦的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈特雷伊公爵的嫡子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾略特·奈特雷伊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈特雷伊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以印有我家徽的黑色利刃之名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此将你们判罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我们判罪?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是自寻死路!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是为了寻死而拔剑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是先救她出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解毒剂似乎生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快找出口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.67,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找你问话是那之后的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是烦人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会为了你行动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这自恋的矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说你也没比我高多少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 不许吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷宫一般的构造呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直什么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是像那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像自己怎样都无所谓的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个艾德格式的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你简直和圣骑士物语里的艾德格一摸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总结起来就是烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾德格在死前说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不怕受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不畏死亡就是我的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他伤害了支持他的人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该挣扎的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该拒绝死亡的!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:20:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是不想把别人也卷入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被抓也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被杀也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 你伤害了多少人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个只求一死的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的自我牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不过是自我满足
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样就能救谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是想保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丝毫不懂活下来的人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说这么天真的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是把痛苦推给了别人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍视你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们代替你承受这份痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不想失去不顾自己死活的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才说了一半
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去你谁都保护不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无视自己生命的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没资格保护别人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}放弃自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}摆出一副悲剧人物的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:21:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了…烦死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:22:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤害自己又伤害别人 你打算就这么活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}被否定。不被期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}去陪小猫咪一起玩吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.56,0:23:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}我一个人受伤就够了……!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.33,0:23:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}我们是好朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.21,0:23:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}我还能继续向前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.50,0:24:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}告诉我! 使用染血黑兔力量的方法!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}回答我 杰克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&}下回 泪之池